description:
Overview:   This series of uploads constitutes the sum total of the very earliest
            digital rips, released between late 2011 and the beginning of organized
            wide distribution in April 2012 - excluding those which, or superior
            versions of which, have already been torrented separately.

            It is a much-diminished "update" of last year's original torrent,
           <a href=" https://thepiratebay.se/torrent/9539599" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> https://thepiratebay.se/torrent/9539599</a>   , due to the exclusion of
            everything that's been superseded in the meantime.
 
            The tally of remaining titles is 17, and I couldn't quite make up my
            mind on whether to re-post those as a single bundle, like last time
            (that being more in the spirit of an "archive"), or separately as
            ordinary torrents. As a compromise between the two, I'm now posting it
            as a multi-part bundle, broken down by publisher. :)



Contains:   The Mission        (2011)      (Digital-TPB-1280) (Zone-Empire)

            Avengelyne 001-006 (2011-2012) (Digital-1280)     (Empire)
